casebody.data:
No. 665,

Misc.

Relford v. Commandant, U. S. Disciplinary Barracks, Ft. Leavenworth. Solicitor General Gris-wold, Assistant Attorney General Wilson, Beatrice Rosenberg, and Roger A. Pauley for respondent.

C. A. 10th Cir. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted limited to retroactivity and scope of O’Callahan v. Parker, 395 U. S. 258, and case transferred to appellate docket.
